<doc id="679325" wikidata="Q3219740" url="?curid=679325" title="Laval Centre">
<text>Laval Centre (; formerly known as Laval-des-Rapides) was a federal electoral district in Quebec, Canada, that was represented in the House of Commons of Canada from 1979 to 2004.

It was created as &quot;Laval-des-Rapides&quot; riding in 1976 from parts of Laval, Ahuntsic, Dollard and Duvernay ridings.

It was renamed &quot;Laval Centre&quot; in 1990.

It was abolished in 2003 when it was redistributed between Laval and Marc-Aurèle-Fortin ridings.

