<doc id="679327" wikidata="Q3219743" url="?curid=679327" title="Laval West">
<text>Laval West (; formerly known as Mille-Iles and Laval) was a federal electoral district in Quebec, Canada, that was represented in the House of Commons of Canada from 1979 to 2004.

It was created as the riding of &quot;Mille-Iles&quot; in 1976 from parts of Laval riding. It was renamed &quot;Laval&quot; in 1977, and &quot;Laval West&quot; in 1990.

In 2003, the riding was abolished when it was redistributed into Laval and Laval—Les Îles ridings.

